Everyone who is interested in getting into Singapore universities check this out! 👇😉
If you are 17 years old (and above) and plan to pursue your higher education in Singapore or other overseas universities, SCI has an exciting offer for you.
Hurry up, as there can be only 10 lucky students! 💃🏍🏎
First 10 students registered for the preparatory course for ‘A’ level examination will get a FREE MacBook and S$2000 discount off course fee.😱🎁👏😄🎉
In order to have higher chances of getting into Singapore universities or other overseas universities. students should score their best GCE 'A' level results. To help international students achieve this academic goal SCI thoroughly prepares private candidates for the Singapore-Cambridge General Certificate of Education Advanced Level (A-level) examination.
For further information: courseinfo@spring.edu.sg, marketing@spring.edu.sg or tel: (65) 6896 0880 or simply comment "YES" and our coordinators will contact you shortly. #specialoffer #bigpromotion #alevel #studyinsingapore#studyabroad #studyoverseas #preparatorycourse #preparationcourse #giveaway #university #freelaptop #freemacbook  #ilovetostudy #neverstoplearning #gooddeal #studentvisa #studentspass #люблюсингапур #специальноепредложение #скидка #мегаскидка #обучениезарубежом #обучениезаграницей #обучениевсингапуре #подготовительныйкурс #бесплатныйноут #бесплатныйноутбук #ноутвподарок #ноутбуквподарок #университет
